<view class="page transit-location-page"><view class="form-header"><view class="form-header-title">上报在途运输位置</view><view class="form-header-desc">请上传托运车辆当前的地理位置，车商客户可实时查看最新轨迹。</view></view><view class="section"><view class="section-title">定位信息</view><region-select-field wx:if="{{b}}" bindselect="{{a}}" u-i="279348e8-0" bind:__l="__l" u-p="{{b}}"/><view class="field"><text class="label">详细在途位置/路段 <text class="required">*</text></text><view class="{{['picker-display', 'transit-address-display', g && 'disabled']}}" bindtap="{{h}}"><view wx:if="{{c}}" class="address-summary"><text class="address-summary-name">{{d}}</text><text wx:if="{{e}}" class="address-summary-detail">{{f}}</text></view><text wx:else style="color:#9ca3af">在地图上搜索或选择当前位置</text></view></view><view class="field"><text class="label">备注说明</text><block wx:if="{{r0}}"><textarea class="textarea" placeholder="可在此备注当前天气、交通堵塞等特殊在途情况" placeholder-style="color:#9ca3af" value="{{i}}" bindinput="{{j}}"/></block></view></view><address-map-picker wx:if="{{m}}" class="r" u-r="addressMapPicker" bindselect="{{l}}" u-i="279348e8-1" bind:__l="__l" u-p="{{m}}"/><view class="fixed-footer"><button class="primary-btn animate-btn" loading="{{n}}" bindtap="{{o}}"> 上报当前最新位置 </button></view></view>